log
@Send Aviion to same place as Nova II
discussed with jsg
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: le.4,v 1.6 2013/10/15 18:13:53 miod Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2003 Paul Weissmann
.\" All rights reserved.
